OL,6,FJames died in 1902 and over the years
OL,7,Fhis grave showed signs of age. Now,
OL,8,Fahead of the Eisteddfod coming to
OL,9,Ftheir hometown of Pontypridd next
OL,10,Fmonth, local people and businesses
OL,11,Fhave restored the grave to its former
OL,12,Fself.
OL,14,FAngharad Walters was one of them.
