OL,3,CGrave of man who composed Welsh
OL,4,Cnational anthem restored
OL,6,F"I thought that with the Eisteddfod
OL,7,Fbeing in Ponty, that now would be a
OL,8,Fgreat time to do the renovation, so we
OL,9,Fcould celebrate our anthem and pay our
OL,10,Frespects to essentially one of the
OL,11,Fmost important people in Welsh
OL,12,Fhistory." she said. Businesses in
OL,13,FAberdare paid for the restoration.
OL,15,FBusinesses in Aberdare paid for the
OL,16,Frestoration which was carried out by
OL,17,FIvor Phillips Sculptors and Angharad
OL,18,Fhopes the new grave will boost
OL,19,Fvisitors to the town.
